{"type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": "I need to add a new user account and create a new filesystem partition through MachineConfig. I plan to use the MachineConfigDaemon's in-place update mechanism so that the nodes pick up both the new user and the new filesystem without requiring a full reprovision. Can you help me write a MachineConfig that adds a user under passwd.users and defines a new filesystem under storage.filesystems?"}, "timestamp": "2026-06-22T21:26:06.946Z"}
